    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a superlative example of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in an impeccable state that challenges the standards of the showroom floor. Every facet of this motorcar\u2014from its mirror-finish exterior to its pristine, untouched cabin\u2014reflects a history of fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the connoisseur who accepts only the finest. We invite serious inquiries to experience a vehicle that remains as striking today as the day it was commissioned.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
