      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, mint condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so the paint is flawless and the interior is totally spotless. It drives like a dream and has been super well-loved. I\u2019m looking for a new home for it where it\u2019ll be just as appreciated. Drop me a message if you want to take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
