    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a showroom-grade E92 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. This example features the high-revving S65 V8 with its signature eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, the rod bearing service and throttle actuators have been proactively addressed. Power is delivered via the lightning-fast 7-speed M-DCT to a Variable M Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and the weight-saving carbon fiber roof remains pristine. Finished in original Alpine White over Novillo leather, this vehicle displays zero paint correction needs and a documented service history that validates its concours-level preservation.",
